{"tid":206022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"性本惡定性本善","createTime":"2017-04-18T07:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T10:55:35.000Z","uid":80761,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19f2c2acdf5c555bb0751fb5e113296e1dac0ee3","tid":206022,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"性本惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n性本善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d371343e170e99f204e58157855c2274c89cec56","tid":206022,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"性本淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229d8c30a3c5e8f11bef1063446c4e715997c619","tid":206022,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性本淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淫算唔算惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c53debc5fc32c9fa7702c2c60933715bf56da35","tid":206022,"uid":42199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"善點定義 惡點定義 點解上帝/神係善嘅化身 我覺得人性本自然 屬中性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ffef763658d8a0203287c722c456f86cb628ab","tid":206022,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>善點定義 惡點定義 點解上帝/神係善嘅化身 我覺得人性本自然 屬中性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n善應該係指有慈悲憐憫之心等等既美德<br />\n而惡就應該係指貪婪、淫邪、自私等等<br />\n上帝/神係善既化身因為聖經/其他宗教既書籍記載上帝/神會無私咁幫助人而唔會作取一啲陷人於不義既行為 好似係<br />\n利申：非耶撚"},{"pid":"63fc7165ee8edd9bb6e067d57114e0afb73bfdec","tid":206022,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"性本惡<br />\n一出世都會爭寵 爭玩具 假如有兄弟姊妹"},{"pid":"8a8e356572b74334d197abd6b310879d3c0d53b7","tid":206022,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"性本無知"},{"pid":"c9223d889b5d748e7c200812f6d8b8aa47e73235","tid":206022,"uid":86873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a990ca088793badd5e34e469b00dea2c69c1074","tid":206022,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性本惡<br />\n一出世都會爭寵 爭玩具 假如有兄弟姊妹</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但點解儒家思想所主張既性本善可以堅持到咁耐？我諗當中一定有佢既原因 所以先開post討論吓"},{"pid":"a015113dc8cf853d357ceb12d05b7f506539ffd1","tid":206022,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"大戰在即<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e801cd9c353ac5ec356d7c4ba7e651606696b1c4","tid":206022,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性本無知</blockquote><br />\n絲打意思係指人既行為同心態取決於佢既生活環境所影響？"},{"pid":"06be98f09d051f5cd4d1a7fab31acf1a421d6199","tid":206022,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大戰在即<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歡迎眾巴絲打熱烈討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc088726912f9d5ca267a7410adc228c1e6739b","tid":206022,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性本惡<br />\n有時會想身邊既人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講吓有咩原因令到你咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5756e2f5cb7631e4ea16bc16c9f948baebb4c70a","